1.m_mText: "Look forward and sever all doubt."
"The curtain falls."
"Sorry, looks like I'll have to break that promise..."
"Win or lose, I must survive."
"Is this a blessing or a curse?"
"Seeking light within the abyss."
"Let's keep moving forward."
"Here again... Is this where I'm meant to be?"
"Will I ever be free of the shackles of the past?"
"The Black Blood... Has it been suppressed?"
"I see, so this is the true power of blood."
"What's come over me, lost in thought while gazing at my reflection."
"So this is what it feels like to connect with others..."
"I don't know if I like it, but I don't dislike this anticipation."
"I can sense that I'm one step closer to understanding my 'true self'."
"I should no longer dwell on the forgotten 'past', but instead pursue the unknown 'future'."
"Who am I? The place where I belong... is it by your side?"
"I feel like I'm gradually beginning to understand you, the other me."
"Sorry, my head hurts a bit. I still tend to forget some important things."
"Is it an illusion? The silver seems to have become more vibrant..."
"Is this... some kind of ritual to establish a connection of memories?"
"Interlocking our fingers, like making a wish."
"I shall stand here and repel any foe that dares approach."
"Come at me!"
"I must not fall..."
"Leave it to me!"
"Wings of the Aegis!"
"In defense, I attack. In retreat, I advance."
"My shield is a stalwart fortress."
"I'll stand firm against the enemies before us!"
"I've been waiting for you. Come, let us begin!"
"My shield... it has become even sturdier."
"I entrust my life to my shield!"
"You assigned me to stand guard? Understood."
"I shall not let you down."
"For me? But... why?"
"This shield will never fall!"
"Without someone to protect, a shield loses its purpose."
"Defending isn't just about self-perservation, it's also about creating opportunities to strike back... Don't you agree?"
"Without the blade in your hand, my shield might weep..."
"Are you performing some kind of ritual?"
"...I need to ask someone what this gesture actually means."
"The purpose of a defender is to exhaust the attacker's strength, while your purpose is to crush the enemy."
"Shields are actually quite fragile. Once cracked, they cannot be easily repaired."
"Let blossoms adorn your final act!"
"Don't underestimate me!"
"Don't look..."
"Allow me to lend you a hand."
"A natural progression of my power."
"Witness the true might of Blood Augmentation!"
"Defeating opponents of this caliber is hardly worth bragging about."
"You again? I suppose we're accomplices by fate."
"What took you so long? You lack the awareness befitting a Vassal of mine!"
"Hey, Vassal, make more offerings to me."
"Mmm...my body feels warmer..."
"Hey, how long are you going to keep me waiting?"
"Hmph, I guess this will do for now."
"Th-this is for me!?"
"Well, aren't you becoming quite considerate..."
"Don't let me keep drowning in this hope that you might be my sunshine."
"Do you have that much free time?"
"Occasionally... spending time listening to you isn't so bad... just occasionally!"
"Hmph, didn't I say not to bother me if there's nothing important?"
"So warm... *cough* You’re spared for today, but only today."
"...Do I need to personally teach you a lesson about manners?"
"Hey! You did that on purpose, didn't you?! You may be my Vassal, but don't push your luck..."
"Guide the stars of the past, bathe in the moonlight of yesteryear."
"Lunar Protection!"
"This too is part of life..."
"It is fate."
"As you wish."
"Cause and effect intertwine, all things cycle."
"Tis the right time, according to fate."
"Allow me to accompany you."
"If you become lost, follow the moonlight."
"The Tempus flows on..."
"Upstream, against the river of time."
"I have long grown accustomed to waiting."
"I shall meet these expectations."
"I am grateful for your generosity."
"The signs have manifested."
"Ah... I always knew this day would come."
"Is there anything I can help you with?"
"I've noticed you've been smiling more lately."
"Perhaps even beneath this mask is not the real me."
"If possible, please... allow me to remove the mask myself."
"This is not the time for games."
"This indescribable feeling... Could this also be a revelation?"
"May the wind grant you mercy!"
"Target acquired."
"I was... so close."
"Target locked!"
"For the mission."
"The moonlight shall guide the wind's path."
"My arrows never miss their mark."
"I will provide support from the back!"
"Unwavering focus is the key to striking every target."
"I can now spot targets clearly from even greater distances."
"With the power of focus, I shall not fear even the most numerous foes."
"Patience is crucial in waiting for the moment when prey lets its guard down."
"My arrow is nocked and ready."
"I accept your thoughtful gesture."
"Mutual understanding is an experience I've never had before. I will deeply contemplate its meaning."
"I never imagined meeting you this way, but... perhaps it's the only way I can break free from my former self."
"If you have some free time, come train with me."
"Returning to the moon... Such a noble ideal. Allow me to be your pillar of support."
"Hehe, shouldn't it be the other way around? I'm older than you, you know?"
"The warmth of your palm... I'm sorry, may I close my eyes for a moment?"
"Are you interested in archery? I can teach you."
"I'm not very familiar with the world beyond archery, but... I'm willing to explore it together with you."
"Born of desire, death by greed."
"Leave it to me."
"Did I mess up...?"
"Ready to serve at your command."
"Is this part of my job too?"
"It seems just cleaning is no longer enough."
"Tidying up rooms is still more of a challenge."
"Ami Landis, at your service for the duration of this voyage."
"Welcome back. I've prepared your room for you."
"I suppose I'll get a bit serious."
"So you need me to protect you after all?"
"In the time you've spent daydreaming, I could have already prepared tomorrow's dinner."
"I'm here to clean, not to cause destruction."
"This isn't payment, but a gift?"
"I must live up to these expectations."
"I can see hope because you sheltered me from death."
"Please step aside. The broom can't navigate corners on its own."
"That look on your face... do you have a specific task for me?"
"...Next time, I might accidentally spill hot tea on you. Do be careful."
"Although this isn't part of my job... I'm happy to oblige."
"Is this how you greet people back home?"
"Habits can be terrifying. I've thought about leaving my overprotective guardian, but I've never dared to take the first step."
"Dungeon of my deepest devotion."
"A futile endeavor."
"Perhaps... this is my retribution..."
"I merely plucked it in passing."
"The count has increased."
"Is this already too much for you to bear?"
"What joy is there to be found in such things?"
"Is possessing a heart something to rejoice over?"
"Do you also have things you cannot forget?"
"An unnecessary gesture."
"It is far too late."
"I shall simply remain here, slowly decaying away."
"Still struggling, are we?"
"I appreciate the sentiment, but I'm afraid it fails to pique my interest."
"Truly? My identity... It does not concern you?"
"Never did I imagine we would grow this close... You have given me reason to carry on."
"Mind the distance between us."
"I suppose the occasional indulgence... would not be unforgivable?"
"Are you toying with me?"
"Do you wish to taste the forbidden fruit by my side?"
"You truly have no fear of idle gossip."
"Since you insist, I shan't decline... But don't come to regret it."

"Puppet: Sorry, we only have one item in stock.
 Real self: And that's death."

"Real self: That's not a customer.
 Puppet: Then send them to hell!"
"Puppet: Time to make a run for it..."
"Puppet: All raw materials for my merchandise!"
"Self: Higher efficiency, higher profits."
"Puppet: Today's earnings is quite satisfactory!"

"Self: Did we overdo it?
 Puppet: Oh my, it seems they're out completely!"

"Puppet: Please support our business! Are you here to buy something?
 Self: Or to become the merchandise?"

"Puppet: Come browse our shop, we have a wonderful selection!
 Self: Cash only. No credit."
"Puppet: Is this also a business transaction?"
"Self: It's time for me to repay you."
"Self: ...There aren't many customers."
"Self: One's own abilities is also important."

"Self: I'm sorry.
Puppet: She's actually thanking you!"

"Puppet: How about I give you a discount?
 Self: Don't tell anyone."
"Self: So the merchandise you've been eyeing... is...?"
"Self: Not for sale."
"Self: Constantly offloading goods has its limits, don't you think?"
"Self: The glass says 'do not touch.'"

"Self: ...I'll consider this customer feedback.
  Puppet: Oh my, Miss Bella actually allowed her head to be patted! Dear customer, how much did you spend?!"
"Puppet: It's common sense to wear gloves when handling valuables!"
"Self: The world you see, the power you touch... it's hard for me to let go of such things."
"Come, taste the bitterness of this forbidden fruit."
"Fear makes a fitting decoration for tonight's soirée."
"I shall take my leave for now."
"Let's indulge in a delightful game, shall we?"
"The sacred forbidden fruit is bitter and hard to swallow."
"Filthy lambs, yet their bodies flow with the most delectable blood."
"Victory's fruits possess a flavor all their own."
"I never expected to meet again... No, I should say our reunion was inevitable."
"Is there a task that requires my attention? Or perhaps... you seek to unravel my mysteries?"
"This technology has already reached a state of refined maturity."
"A most welcome surprise. Commendable work."
"Humans are naught but beasts in garments, and gods fare no better."
"Shall we begin the experiment?"
"How unexpected to find myself an invitee. I shall savor this evening."
"Who am I in your eyes, truly?"
"It seems there remains a part of my heart I cannot relinquish."
"Speak not; simply feel the tranquility of this moment..."
"Mortals seek the forgiveness of gods, yet what I desire is to make those gods beg for mine."
"You seem to have changed."
"You remind me more and more of an old acquaintance—perhaps you are he."
"Can you see it? The wine in my hand... a toast to this foolish world."
"Embracing one another may be the way to returning to the other side."
"Watch as time itself is set ablaze!"
"I hope this won't be too agonizing for you."
"Finally, I can rest..."
"Can't I just cheer you on from the sidelines?"
"Don't make me do too much work, alright?"
"When believers get this zealous, it really puts the gods in a bind."
"Good grief... Is it finally over?"
"How bothersome... Guess I should at least say hello."
"We meet again, Noah, my boy."
"Ah, so hot, it burns..."
"Oh? You wish to add more kindling to this undying flame?"
"What should I do to kill some time?"
"It's about time I got to relax too."
"No pain, no gain, but I'll gladly take the latter."
"Aw man, getting too buddy-buddy with you wasn't part of the plan."
"With you around, even work won't be too dull."
"Sigh... what is it now?"
"Putting in a bit of effort once in a while isn't so bad... No, forget what I said."
"The duty of a torch is to burn itself and illuminate the dark ages... I'm just kidding."
"I really wish I could control my own future... At least then, I could slack off with you."
"I found this spot first. Mind going somewhere else?"
"I'm not slacking off, I swear. Just pondering more efficient ways to solve problems... Really."
"How feeble."
"Come forth, my servants!"
"No, I won't accept this..."
"Those who don't know subservience shall be punished!"
"That's more like it!"
"My blood is pumping heartbeats!"
"That was too easy."
"Oh, so you're the one trying to control me?"
"What, you don't look like much at all. Why in the world..."
"Humph, that's it...?"
"Phew... At least that's somewhat of an improvement."
"You dare neglect me?"
"I'm used to this by now."
"At least you know your place."
"You're wasted staying by that person's side."
"Be mine, and I'll give you what she could never."
"I don't recall giving you permission to speak to me so casually."
"Isn't it about time you left her and pledged yourself to me instead?"
"How rude. I should teach you some manners."
"Oh, alright... I suppose I can make an exception and allow you to speak with me."
"The last person who disrespected me ended up in pieces."
"So that's how it is. And here I thought you weren't interested in me."
"Be buried in shadows."
"Playtime is over."
"I see... home..."
"None shall escape."
"The crescent moon grants new life."
"Can you feel the moon's shadow enveloping you?"
"Hmph, is that the best you can do?"
"So you've found me in the shadows. Try to keep up, then."
"Have you also come to enjoy the night's serenity?"
"Let's leave it at that for now."
"I hear the moonlight's whispers..."
"What's on your mind? Speak, and I will take care of it."
"One day, I will eclipse even the sun."
"Is this the appropriate time to express gratitude?"
"The moonlit night seems not quite so cold this evening."
"This restlessness... Why can I not quell it...?"
"Light begets shadow, but the shadow holds no allegiance."
"Even if you were to descend into hell, would you still be willing to accompany me?"
"I am accustomed to dwelling in the shadows. There is no need for you to feel perplexed."
"I have always walked alone, but the moonlight seems to be casting two shadows."
"The feelings in my heart vanished long ago with the moonlight."
"We are both dust under the moonlight, born here and destined to be buried here."
"This is what you get for messing with me!"
"Take this!"
"Strange... I can't get up anymore..."
"I'll take care of these guys!"
"My blood is boiling!"
"Leave the rest to me!"
"This victory, I'll take it."
"This time, I'll risk everything to protect you!"
"Is it my turn to shine? Allow me to solve all your problems!"
"Getting stronger, just as I expected."
"I'm ready for anything!"
"I'm so bored... No, I have to use this time to train!"
"This restlessness... Is it a thirst for battle?"
"Thanks! You've got great taste!"
"Call me if you run into trouble!"
"Um... can I get a bit closer? There's this familiar scent..."
"Hm? Did you call me?"
"I wish I could just have a good cry for once..."
"Ah! Don't sneak up on me like that. I might hurt you."
"If there's a battle, I'm counting on you to watch my back!"
"Hey! Aren't you getting a little too comfortable?"
"How relaxing... Wait, this is no time to rest!"
"Born in light, forged in shadow."
"Fall into darkness."
"Is the long night finally over...?"
"Mourn for your imminent demise."
"Blood merges with shadow."
"What is closer to immortality - eternity, or the void?"
"Even the light can be shrouded by shadows."
"...I dislike really bright places."
"I don't recall calling you... But it seems you have no intention of leaving."
"Mere child's play."
"The deeper the night, the thicker the shadows."
"Even in the absence of light, my shadow persists."
"Is this the weight of shadow?"
"...I'll accept it."
"Stay close to me."
"Do you wish to meld into the shadows with me?"
"I am the shadow."
"Shadow is the opposite of light... yet also its complement."
"Don't presume to touch the shadows."
"Look down at your shadow. In times of loneliness, it's the only thing that will accompany you."
"These shadows beneath your feet - were they born from you, or do you merely cling to their existence?"
"Immersed in darkness, yet refusing to be corrupted... Perhaps you alone are the guiding light."
"Blood-soaked blade whirl!"
"Death approaches you!"
"I cannot rest in peace yet."
"Whose life shall I claim this time?"
"Only slaughter keeps me alert."
"Am I now worthy to face the flames?"
"I've survived once again."
"Surprised? This is what someone driven by hatred and at the end of their rope looks like."
"I completely understand your reaction."
"Not sharp enough yet."
"This power is enough to cut through flames."
"You're the first one who's been able to hold my gaze for so long."
"This is what I've been striving for."
"Speak. What do you want to gain?"
"Do you not fear me?"
"If only I could have met you sooner... as the person I once was."
"You have peculiar tastes."
"It's too late... Yes, it's all too late."
"Curiosity may be the death of you."
"That will only dull my blade."
"I'll stop at nothing to exact my revenge."
"Don't try to dissuade me. This is what I want... even if this body is reduced to ash."
"Feel the scorching heat of the sun!"
"One strike is all it takes!"
"I can't... fall... yet..."
"Leave it to me."
"The mist is slowly clearing."
"The sun rises high."
"This victory belongs to all of us."
"Our reunion is guided by the Lord's will, and... by the light you've shone on my path."
"Come quickly, it's time for prayer. We mustn't keep the Lord waiting."
"The path lies hidden among the stars."
"Let us tread the path illuminated by divine light."
"Walk with me across this narrow and perilous 'bridge'."
"I wonder what will happen. How exciting!"
"You've even chosen a style I like. How thoughtful of you."
"The greatest virtue of humanity is to embrace destiny and illuminate each other."
"This familiar sunset view has become so beautiful. It must be because you're by my side."
"Every day we live is unique and irreplaceable. Cherish the present moment."
"Haha, do you want a reward too?"
"Hmm... Feeling a bit playful, are we?"
"Feeling bored? Come on, let's play our favorite game!"
"Is there somewhere you'd like to go? Just tell me directly."
"Here, give me your hand. I want to take you somewhere, but it's a secret for now. Just the two of us, okay?"
"Wallow in your torment."
"The essence of equilibrium."
"Time to... slumber..."
"Blades drawn."
"Upholding Order's edict."
"I will fulfill your expectations."
"None shall escape my blade."
"I shall uphold the divine commandments bestowed upon me."
"Ever ready to slay those who defy order."
"Is this warmth...the divine's embrace?"
"I shall not disappoint you."
"I still linger between life and death."
"My blade grows ever sharper."
"...You have my gratitude."
"You seem to be different from the others."
"In you, I sense a presence akin to that of the divine..."
"Please refrain from touching me. "
"To be close to you in this moment... Forgive my selfishness."
"Is this what you desire?"
"Allow me... to feel warmth once more."
"Keep your distance."
"Am I more than a weapon? It seems I harbor emotions as well."
"This will be the last time you face The Light."
"Be buried in The Light!"
"The light shall never fade; the long night will inevitably break into dawn."
"A wise strategy."
"Ah, the first light of dawn."
"How dare you dim my light."
"Those who dread the dark cannot fathom the Light."
"Eternity is naught but a tomb built from a myriad of ephemeral moments."
"I shall illuminate for you the path to the Light."
"Even the faintest glimmer can pierce the night."
"Only by bathing in the Light can one be reborn."
"Though the world may be consumed by darkness, I shall stand guard until the last twilight."
"So this is light's warmth..."
"I can feel the sincerity in your heart."
"Follow in my footsteps."
"On this journey to pursue the light, will you join me?"
"Ironic, isn't it? Though I chase the light, the armor I wear is so cold..."
"Light and shadow... They always coexist."
"Do you also believe gold to be the most radiant hue?"
"Where light reaches, shadows are born. Perhaps in some corner of my heart, there is darkness that goes unnoticed..."
"How dare you dim my light."
"I see... I see the light..."
"Judgment... comes!"
"Battle... stance!"
"Damage... critical."
"Joining... formation."
"Baptism... complete."
"Armaments... ready."
"Mission... accomplished."
"Silver Cross... has arrived."
"Greetings."
"Enhancement... received."
"Ascension... complete."
"Observing..."
"Ready for transfusion."
"Unable to identify."
"Traces of warmth."
"What is... heart?"
"Unable to respond."
"Show... enthusiasm."
"All is... calm."
"I serve."
"Your actions... perplexing."
"Unknown... feeling."
"Know your place."
"Do not overstep."
"Returning to nature's embrace..."
"Pray, let no innocent creatures be caught in the fray..."
"Draw your weapon when ready."
"It seems I need to get a bit more serious."
"If I cannot secure a victory of this caliber, I would not dare call myself a Knight."
"Let me make one thing clear from the outset - I am a pacifist."
"Hey there, what have you been up to lately?"
"Is it just my imagination, or did I sense something?"
"To protect those worth defending, I must hone my own skills."
"There's nothing better than being able to spend my days in peace and leisure."
"As long as no innocent souls are harmed."
"That's so considerate of you. You have my gratitude."
"Ah, you're the only one who truly understands me."
"In the past, I could only sigh helplessly in the face of death. But now... I will protect everyone."
"You want to know what's beneath the armor? I'm afraid it might startle you."
"You think there's another suit of armor inside this one? Is this what they call... humor?"
"This is not a garlic stalk, it's used to detect enemies."
"Even if you water it, it won't grow."
"Curious, aren't you? Heh, maybe someday, but now is not the time."
"This appearance has brought me much criticism... but I have my reasons. If only they could accept me as you do."
"Listen to fate's solo performance."
"Let the requiem resound."
"I can't... play... anymore..."
"This is quite interesting."
"What's this new trick?"
"The hymns of the temple, a requiem for the departed."
"Is that all? How boring."
"Let me sing you a poem... Nevermind, too troublesome. Let's find something more interesting."
"Kid, come dance to my newly composed tune."
"You're not expecting me to grow taller, are you?"
"What's the use of being tall? They're still not as good as me."
"I'm so bored... Hey, kid, don't pretend you can't hear me!"
"So many people, this should be fun to watch!"
"Ooh, is it something fun to play with?"
"I didn't expect to meet someone so... intriguing."
"Oh dear, don't make me fall in love with this feeling, little one..."
"Doing something even more boring than boredom itself... I suppose that's a form of amusement too."
"All tomorrows look just like yesterdays to me. Thankfully, you've given me a little diversion."
"There's no treasure hidden in my hair, you know. Except your own hand, of course."
"Don't let me get used to this warmth. After all, only the earth can perceive the traces left by the wind."
"That's not for you to touch, little one."
"I'll be kind enough to let you have a glimpse of my little secret today."
"Embrace Order."
"Such are the rules."
"Until the next cycle."
"I refuse all sacrifice."
"The rifts in the world shall be mended."
"Thus, I may bestow blessings upon the people."
"This is the requiem bestowed upon you."
"Kneel and repent. The future you desire lies within my grasp."
"May life be blessed, may humanity flourish, and may order be restored."
"The world's fate grows ever clearer."
"I now stand at the pinnacle of the heavens."
"Even by merely standing here, the future of this world has long been determined."
"It's time to open your eyes and see the truth."
"There is no need for this."
"Let us hearken to the gospel together..."
"If walking alongside you is the preordained future... I am willing to embrace it."
"Life is so fragile, so delicate that even the gentlest touch can cause it to wither."
"Human will were originally one... including yours and mine."
"All things are given order by rules. This is not a constraint, but true freedom."
"Disrupting order is unforgivable, but if it's you, perhaps you can show me a different future."
"I have not granted you permission to act in such a manner."
"The hymn you offer to me bestows worth upon a hollow soul."
"Revel in Death's embrace."
"Kiss of fate."
"Heh... The prophecy of 'Death' is not the end, merely an unavoidable path."
"Now then, unleash the 'The Devil'."
"Hope leads to 'The Star.'"
"I feel the joy of 'The Sun.'"
"With 'The Chariot' in hand, victory is inevitable."
"Who do you see standing before you? 'The Magician'? Or Jacintha Dalcarlo?"
"From atop 'The Tower', all I can see is destruction... A vision of the apocalypse."
"It seems I've drawn the 'Strength' card. So be it."
"I see... a new 'World.' How utterly fascinating."
"Now that you wield 'The Staff', I'm curious to see how you'll use this power."
"I hear the prayer of the 'Hierophant.'"
"What an adorable little trinket."
"You wish to exchange the 'Ace of Cups' with me? It would be my pleasure."
"Is it a 'lover' you desire... or is it me?"
"Perfect timing. Why don't you keep me company for a spell? I'll be sure to... properly compensate you."
"Under the silver glow of the 'The Moon', the future you see... is there a place for me in it?"
"Are you the 'Fool'... or the 'Hermit'...?"
"Hmm, a Tarot spread I can't decipher... How intriguing. What is your name?"
"Oh my, this simply won't do. It seems we both need to exercise a bit of 'temperance' now, don't we?"
"Everyone loves secrets, but no one likes their secrets pried into... What about you?"
"Please... don't stand in my way."
"I can't falter now!"
"Turned to... salt crystals..."
"Are you... sure?"
"What a strange sensation..."
"Such warmth... I have to keep moving."
"I still have a long way to go…"
"Can someone like me really stand beside you?"
"Being here… feels right."
"I must do better..."
"Is it right… to entrust this power to me?"
"Do I... belong here? Ah, I was just thinking aloud."
"I won’t fail the faith placed in me."
"F-for me? I'll keep it safe."
"S-sorry... could you stay with me a little longer?"
"So this is what it feels like… to walk with someone."
"I was born to bear my family's hopes... but what are mine?"
"This warmth… My heart knew what it longed for all along."
"I-Is there something on my head?"
"You seem to... always give me unexpected warmth."
"I keep dreaming of the future… but duty always pulls me back."
"My duty kept me lost in the past... and you're the key to my future."
"In the cycle of rebirth, turn to dust along with time itself."
"The end of one world is merely the dawn of another."
"So my consciousness... fades away..."
"How dreadfully dull."
"Perhaps there is still a chance to break free from this cycle."
"I hope to find at least a modicum of enjoyment in this..."
"An inevitable outcome."
"I am but a wanderer, blind to the future, endlessly roaming at the edge of time."
"Do you wish to glimpse the secrets of time through me?"
"I've experienced this sensation before..."
"The consciousness deep within my soul gradually awakens."
"Even the hardest stone will be ground to sand by time... as will I."
"The hands of the pocket watch have turned."
"I'll accept it for now. This, too, is part of the rules."
"So my heart still beats after all..."
"It seems you have freed me from the shackles of time."
"I hope my presence doesn't make you uncomfortable."
"The time frozen around me seems to flow once more..."
"Could you maintain some distance?"
"Time has no end, only the solitude of eternity."
"My ties to this world were severed by time long ago."
"One day, I shall open my eyes at the boundless edge of time."
"Turn against the flow of time, and return what once was!"
"Moonlight Revelation."
"A momentary lapse in judgment..."
"As you wish."
"Reshaping an incomplete past."
"This is the future you've bestowed upon me."
"We still have a long journey ahead."
"I have always awaited the arrival of the 'present,' woven from past and future."
"Is something troubling you? You can confide in me."
"I can clearly see the path before me."
"May this power lead me to the Other Side."
"Perhaps uncertainty is bliss, for only those with a path to follow can stray from it."
"As I am now, can I reach the moon that's before my eyes?"
"I will cherish this surprise."
"We are all solitary beings, yet when our paths intertwine, destiny takes shape."
"From this day forward, I shall no longer support you from behind, but walk beside you as an equal."
"Patience. Await the opportune moment, and success will come naturally."
"Perhaps I can become the night that shelters the moonlight, quietly waiting at the end of the road."
"Please don't look into my eyes, at least... not right now."
"What I fear is knowing I will lose something and being powerless to stop it..."
"Until the path is clear, this is not the time to daydream."
"Allow me a glimpse into the future. I want to know if, at the end of time, I still exist in your memories."
"Listen to the seedlings breaking through the soil."
"Feel the pulse of life."
"I shall... wither..."
"I'll do my best."
"Life sprouts here."
"I've become more vibrant."
"There's still a gap between knowledge and real battle."
"If needed, I can share my knowledge with you."
"Would you accompany me to the herb garden?"
"Knowledge is boundless."
"An enlightening experience."
"In my leisure, I also enjoy quietly contemplating things."
"How does this work exactly?"
"As a token of gratitude, I will mend your wounds next time."
"Having you by my side puts me at ease."
"I never thought I'd care for someone else like this..."
"Are you feeling unwell?"
"If you don't mind, please close your eyes and listen to the whispers of the flowers and plants."
"That's not very polite, you know."
"So this is how the plants feel when I touch them..."
"Ignorance is a sin in itself."
"Your thirst for knowledge is stronger than I anticipated."
"Be lost in the dream."
"Do you still remember this dream?"
"I'm sinking... into the shadow..."
"Gone with the dream."
"Embrace the dream."
"Wake from the illusion."
"That was no dream."
"I have heard your call, master."
"What beautiful dream would you like to have today?"
"New dreams, new inspirations."
"Classical, romantic, realistic, fantasy... I've collected so many dreamscapes."
"Dozing off already? I haven't even sung my lullaby..."
"Out of everyone, you chose me?"
"Is this my reward for completing my task?"
"Is it time to take the next step?"
"I am with you, until eternity."
"Ah, no, it's just... this is a little sudden."
"If that is your wish, I can oblige."
"Would you like me to help you fall asleep?"
"For my next reward... I'd like to fall asleep together and dream."
"Are you practicing? It's more effective to set the reward and punishment first."
"This is what you desire? Then... I shall weave the perfect dream for you."
"I shall dedicate the finale of life's symphony to this dance."
"Heed the final cadence."
"I yearn to leap once more..."
"Allow me to present the dance."
"My legs have grown even more nimble."
"As a slave to music, I can finally dance without end."
"The dance must not end here."
"Let us celebrate our first encounter with a dance."
"I've devised a new dance step. Would you care to be my first audience?"
"What a marvelous sensation."
"These legs can carry me to even greater distances."
"Don't you think dance can guide the soul to break free from the flesh and find true paradise?"
"New inspiration has come to me."
"What a gentle audience you are... Then I shall accept your gift."
"Join me in the dance."
"In the future... I wish to show you the dance steps hidden deep within my memories."
"My body has been feeling a bit stiff lately... Could it be because I haven't moved in a while?"
"Don't take your hand away. I want you to lead me as I continue dancing."
"Interrupting someone's thoughts is not very polite."
"If this were the end of my life, I would still want to use all my strength... to offer you one last dance."
"Next time, remember to buy a ticket first."
"You're in the VIP seat now. Your eyes should be fixed on me."
"For the greater good."
"Purge the filth."
"I was not enough..."
"Then let us begin."
"There's nothing worth celebrating."
"Let us quicken our pace."
"Let us honor the sacrifices that led us here."
"Black Blood can be cured. But there are many things that can't be."
"Do you need me to examine you?"
"...That's not necessary."
"To gain something... something else must be given."
"Are you feeling unwell? You've just been standing there."
"Life has grown even more burdensome."
"This is for me? Thank you."
"Come closer. Let me feel the warmth of your presence."
"Promise me you'll stay safe, okay? I couldn't bear to see your wounds."
"The world is constantly being renewed, and destroyed."
"...Forgive me. Now is not the time to let go of all restraint."
"I don't mind revealing my true face, but it's better for both of us if I don't."
"The sensation of your touch... I shall engrave it deeply in my heart."
"Humans cannot resist the will of the gods."
"Perhaps we were fated to never truly understand one another."
"Witness the advent of flame!"
"Ignite the darkness."
"Blaze for me once more..."
"I guess I'll get a bit serious."
"You call me the 'Beguiler,' yet offer something so irresistible?"
"Well, there goes my excuse for slacking off..."
"You've certainly caused me quite a bit of trouble."
"As long as the flame still burns, even death can be warm... Care to try?"
"Accursed by flame, condemned to burn until the end of days."
"Phew, this fiery passion is getting intense!"
"We witness the blaze of life burning bright, until time turns it all to ashes."
"Your gaze feels even hotter than my flames. Is it getting warm in here, or is it just me?"
"This time, perhaps we can change the future..."
"What a hassle... Picking out a gift in return is no easy task, you know?"
"Once, someone tried to fly toward the sun. Can you guess what befell them?"
"I never imagined it would be you by my side... No, I'm glad it is you."
"Careful, it's quite scorching."
"What is birthed from the flames is not civilization, but countless wars."
"Ah... I have already drifted off to sleep. All I utter now is but sleep talk."
"The gods are merely tools to reach the future. And as tools, there must be someone to wield them."
"Admiration is the furthest cry from understanding. You have my regrets."
"What I yearn for are not followers dependent on me, but kindling that can burn alongside me."
"This shall be the final requiem."
"Divine retribution approaches."
"Do not mourn for me..."
"The Lance of God awaits here."
"With this power, I shall slay our enemies more efficiently."
"My body seems to be growing restless..."
"Awaiting the next Task."
"The Church gave me a title, but the children’s voices gave me my name."
"Do you have a new task?"
"I have been blessed."
"The feeling deep within my mind... so strange."
"Who... am I, really?"
"This scene feels oddly familiar..."
"I will treasure this."
"May I... come a little closer?"
"This strange impulse in my heart... What could it be?"
"Are you expressing your friendliness?"
"Your scent... it seems to awaken memories within me. Please, would you come closer?"
"This sensation feels strange to me."
"I can't remember who I am, but... I don't think I belong to the Church."
"What do you expect from this cold, lifeless body?"
"I never thought my heart, long grown cold, could burn so fiercely again..."
"I'll send you to your grave."
"There's no escape."
"This humiliation... how fitting..."
"I see the target."
"I want more."
"Have I earned the right to live?"
"Mission accomplished. Target has been eliminated."
"I'm Selena Dalma, hired assassin on occasion... Oh, you're glaring at me..."
"Oh... Wh-What a coincidence... running into you here..."
"You're using your precious resources on me? Hmm..."
"Even someone like me... I will follow... No, pursue you for life!"
"I'm being ignored... Okay, I don't mind. Not at all."
"Is... is this really happening?"
"Is this a bounty? Strange, I haven't taken any jobs recently."
"Really? You better not be lying... Liars have to swallow a thousand arrows."
"No one has ever been this kind to me... Thank you for giving me a place to return to."
"And just what do you think you're doing?"
"So, um, when vampires bite people... isn't it kind of intimate? Don't you... get embarrassed?"
"Hmph, you'd best watch your back at night!"
"Don't tug on my scarf... Ah, it's coming loose! Waahhh..."
"You'll pay for this."
"Hey, we all have to make due with what we were given, okay?"
"Cycles entwined, all consumed and laid to rest."
"The flying arrow, moving yet unmoving."
"Darkness... is where I truly belong..."
"We shall release them from their torment."
"Birth is not the beginning, death not the end."
"Unforgotten, the cycle endures eternally."
"No death is without regret, only cold oblivion."
"So I never lost my memories, I just chose not to remember."
"Only by breaking free from the gravity of our past can we soar towards the starry sea of our future."
"Growth is the process of discovering oneself."
"I should no longer run from my true self."
"What's come over me, lost in thought while gazing at my reflection."
"Am I the one who remains stagnant?"
"Sometimes, one should reward oneself."
"The joy of a long life lies in rediscovering oneself time and again."
"To truly love one's fate and embrace oneself, that is the greatest courage of all."
"It takes considerable resolve to touch the embodiment of death."
"One such as I should no longer get close to anyone...except myself."
"Is the silver-white a symbol of decay, or of emptiness?"
"You have always been able to see the world through my eyes. Now, at last, I can see yours as well."
"Do you also experience this feeling of being watched from places hard to comprehend?"
"You are me in another place. This resonance of memories is the best proof."
"Purify the tainted souls."
"Repent at your leisure!"
"Justice... shall never perish..."
"The hour of execution has come."
"All is for the sake of justice."
"This power shall root out the wicked."
"Before the face of justice, what chance do evil and intrigue stand?"
"Nothing can shake my conviction."
"Setting the chaotic world right... That is my life's purpose!"
"Another step forward."
"I'm getting closer to... the ultimate answer."
"Have you also begun to feel lost in the darkness of this world?"
"It's time to get ready..."
"Oh, this is... for me?"
"Are you also searching for justice?"
"Perhaps I should rethink the meaning of justice... through your perspective."
"Oh you wanna train together? I'm afraid I don't have the time at the moment."
"Your hand... Could you keep holding mine a little longer? I fear I may lose my way..."
"These injuries are nothing. I'm strong!"
"I sense a different kind of justice in you... I see... True justice is tested after one gains power."
"An alchemist's tools aren't for prying eyes!"
"You've earned my approval. I shall let you witness the source of this explosive power!"
"Repent before the thunder!"
"I shall crush you with my might!"
"Fall back for now."
"It's my turn."
"Relish the thrill of battle."
"This feeling... Are there any worthy opponents to fight?"
"The battle's over already?"
"I hope you can put up a fight, or it won't be any fun."
"This time, I hope you can fight by my side until the very end."
"I feel the power you've bestowed upon me."
"The sword stands upon a mound of bones, fulfilling an oath to the dead."
"Are you trying to find my weakness?"
"Will you join me in this sacred rite?"
"Why are you giving this to me?"
"My heart yearns for baptism by battle."
"With you, perhaps I can really feel alive."
"From the moment one steps onto the battlefield, the Lord shows no favoritism to anyone."
"Peace nurtures the seeds of war, yet war, in turn, nurtures peace."
"When humanity is tainted by evil, the Lord shall bring punishment through the fires of war."
"I strive to hold back the tides of war, to keep you safe behind me."
"Only those who have strayed know the value of the right path."
"It seems the battlefield you seek is elsewhere... No matter, allow me to accompany you."
"I grant you a proper death."
"Ignorance, too, is a form of evil."
"So this is... Death..."
"We fight to bring peace."
"I still have strength to spare."
"I'm in my element."
"We're victorious... for the moment."
"Just Ottavia will do. The rest is irrelevant."
"My wish is simple: let the wicked die as they deserve, and the good meet their end with grace. Nothing more."
"There is still room to improve."
"Have I surpassed the old man now...? No, never mind."
"You're quite content to sit there, aren't you? Well, don't blame me if I take the lead."
"Oh? I didn't know this was possible."
"It's not exactly novel, but I can tell you put some thought into it. Thanks."
"You're proving to be somewhat trustworthy."
"Hey, don't go dying on me. You make a pretty good adventuring partner."
"Let's hope your death isn't too unsightly."
"I won't let you die for now, but this doesn't mean you're absolved."
"Chivalrous? You flatter me. I simply cannot stand injustice."
"After meeting you, I am even more convinced that a meaningless life is not destined, but an excuse for the weak-willed."
"You've heard tales of my swordsmanship? Haha, perhaps you heard wrong."
"I forget you're quite skilled with a sword too. Why don't you go inherit my title? You're far more suited than I."
"This is proof of my return from hell!"
"You're finished!"
"I'm still... not ready..."
"It's finally my turn!"
"The past me is gone."
"With this power, I can protect everyone!"
"It's not enough... I've yet to reach my limit!"
"The inverse butterfly flutters its wings, bringing both clear skies and tumultuous storms..."
"Don't come too close. I don't want you to get hurt."
"Have I still not adapted to this power...?"
"From now on, I'll be the one protecting you!"
"If I could choose again, perhaps I would have stayed here as the girl I once was."
"These enhancements are woefully inadequate..."
"I will treasure this."
"I've always been right here by your side."
"Let time stand still for a moment. I want to savor this lingering warmth."
"Only bitterness and regret remain, buried deep in my memories."
"It's the pain of the past that reminds me I'm still alive."
"Don't move. I'm... afraid I might lose control."
"Though I've been born anew, my heart remains unchanged."
"Now's not the time for such things."
"If I can be of assistance to you... perhaps this power isn't as terrible as I once believed."
"Steel yourself to bear the weight of life."
"Life flows."
"From deadwood, new buds shall sprout..."
"What restless creatures they are."
"It seems this vessel is not destined to wither yet."
"Can you smell it? This is the fragrance of life's fruit."
"Bury them well and let nature embrace their souls."
"All things in this world will eventually turn to dust, absorb the rain and dew, and sprout anew. That is life."
"Come closer, and let me whisper nature's secrets to you."
"The tender shoots are about to break through the earth..."
"Now I can linger in this world a while longer."
"One must savor these rare moments of tranquility."
"Nature is calling out to my soul..."
"Thank you for the things you have painstakingly prepared for me."
"Plants are not without hearts..."
"Our lives seem to be intertwined like branches."
"This form marks the humanity I've forsaken."
"Life has a beginning and an end, yet plants can endure eternally..."
"Humans... such despicable creatures. Become my sustenance."
"Plants can shatter the shackles of time and grasp the breadth of the soul."
"Linger a moment longer, and you will feel the resonance of the plants."
"What you touch is not flesh, but the life flowing beneath the skin."
"Plunge into the turbid currents of fate."
"Cease your struggle."
"I'm... so cold..."
"Desire beckons."
"The chill fades away..."
"Descending into greater depths..."
"It's time to return."
"Would you like to see my homeland, buried deep beneath the waves?"
"Are you sure it's alright to be wandering around when there's still so much work to be done?"
"You really won't let me rest, will you?"
"Sigh... let me handle the troublesome stuff from now on."
"You keep staring at me. Is there something you need?"
"Very well, I'll humor you for a bit."
"Since you prepared this for me, I'll accept it."
"I felt your warmth once again."
"If one cannot break free from the shackles of desire, then one must learn to live with its presence... Right?"
"Being handsy is not a desirable quality."
"Eek...! Does teasing me really bring you such joy? What a terrifying fetish."
"Rest assured, no dust will settle on my head."
"You want to share the burden of my thoughts? With you here, I've learned to let go of them."
"There's nothing here but darkness. You should know that."
"There was once only emptiness here, but it is precisely because of that, that it can hold this warmth."
"A blunt axe be all I need to claim thy head!"
"'Tis the soul-piercin' chill from the very depths!"
"This aunciente one...yields not...!"
"Allow this auncient one to enlighten thee on the nature of power."
"Such pure, unbridled might of the spirit..."
"The Soul is the most perfect form of life."
"While this auncient one draws breath, ne'er shall victory be ceded!"
"The strong devour the weak. Only the victors will be remembered."
"Ah, tranquility... it's been too long."
"This meagre enhancement isn't even enough to pick my teeth with."
"This ancient soul still burns!"
"Speak your mind, if you've aught to say."
"Not enough... I need more!"
"You have my thanks."
"Is this the resonance of souls?"
"Hmph, you are the second to earn my respect. Or perhaps, you were also the first."
"Shall I help you shed the shackles of the flesh as well...?"
"The secret to immortality... does it pique your interest?"
"What truly defines a person - their physical form, or their soul?"
"Your gaze reminds this old warrior of the days when I still possessed mortal flesh."
"This armor can offer you naught but cold."
"Were it not for the shackles of this armor, perhaps I could understand the likes of you."
"I apologize, but you will fall beneath my blade."
"Please grant me courage."
"This can't be the end..."
"Crush the enemy."
"I... shall not waver."
"This sword will cut through everything."
"I have protected once more."
"Clive Ganelon, Gravekeeper of the Forbidden Grounds."
"I wield my blade to protect friends and kin."
"My sword has grown a bit stronger."
"This power was born solely for protection, nothing more."
"Until the day this greatsword rusts, I will let none come to harm."
"My body... it creaks and groans..."
"This kindness, I shall cherish for a lifetime!"
"So this is what lies within your heart..."
"Henceforth, I shall fight and perish for your sake."
"If humans were to don the pelts of beasts, could they still retain a human heart..."
"You... have known all along, haven't you? That this is an unbreakable cycle."
"I shall guard the forbidden grounds, for all eternity..."
"Every time I open my eyes, it marks the beginning of a tragedy. But this time... I have you by my side."
"Breathing tears through my flesh like a blade, but it also reminds me of my own cowardice."
"I entrust my future to you."
"I too... can protect everyone!"
"I can't stop now..."
"I'm sorry..."
"Are you... sure?"
"My body... It feels different somehow."
"Does this mean I'm a grown-up now?"
"Is this a dream? Did I... really win?"
"If there's anything I can do... No, please let me help you!"
"What do I need to do to get stronger... Ah! It's, it's nothing, just talking to myself..."
"Will this make me stronger...?"
"I've finally caught up to you."
"You've been quiet... Did I do something wrong?"
"I have to keep pushing myself!"
"I-is this really for me?"
"Please don't be so kind to me..."
"I won't let you down... I absolutely won't!"
"I fear the darkness, yet I cannot touch the light."
"Could you... let me feel your warmth again?"
"If only I had more time, perhaps I could truly grow and mature."
"I tiptoe to be closer to you, but you're still out of reach."
"Do you think I'm just some kid too?!"
"To protect everyone... I must become stronger."
"The grand finale, by yours truly!"
"Follow me, I know the one true way."
"Even in sinking, such beauty..."
"The El Dorado sets sail in all her splendor!"
"Captivated by my valiant prowess on the battlefield, are you?"
"How beautiful... the El Dorado never disappoints."
"The El Dorado returns, her hold overflowing with the spoils of victory!"
"Impress me, and I may consider allowing you aboard the El Dorado."
"Don't dare avert your gaze. Miss my splendor, and you'll regret it dearly."
"More power..."
"Tell me, was that gold you saw, or just my brilliance?"
"What's this? Has my irresistible charm struck you speechless?"
"This place could use a serious refit."
"You should know that such meager attempts at appeasement will hardly suffice."
"Speak, then. What reward do you seek from me?"
"The show is about to begin… shall we walk into it together?"
"Oh? Do you covet a bespoke ensemble such as mine?"
"Like the silk? I'll send a set your way."
"You desire a self-portrait of mine? Fret not, for I can indulge this trifling request of yours."
"My future is but a dream of endlessly prayer to return to the bygone days."
"Gold... 'Tis a thing of beauty, is it not? Dazzling, never fading - precisely what I seek."
"Gold lasts forever... and maybe what we've built does too."
"Consider it an honor to be granted death by my hand!"
"Resistance is futile."
"Is this... pain?"
"Become my nourishment."
"This pleasure is truly unforgettable."
"Let us begin constructing a paradise of flesh and blood."
"Cattle, grovel on the ground like the livestock you are."
"As the first to dare approach me, perhaps I should grant you a reward... How about some human blood?"
"May I have a taste of you?"
"The blood wails in agony..."
"This sense of fulfillment, of being filled to the brim... I crave more."
"Ah, the melodious sound of blood coursing through the body. It's music to my ears."
"The limit hasn't been reached. Not yet."
"I desire you more than this trivial offering."
"Do you wish to offer your blood to me?"
"You shan't escape my grasp. Not until I have the world in my hands."
"If even the gods had flesh and blood... I wonder, what exquisite flavor would they yield?"
"Humans, gods, the Church... nothing more than pieces of flesh destined to rot away."
"Blood is my only craving."
"Stand by my side and witness how I toy with this world."
"Don't forget, your ability to stay by my side is the reward I've bestowed upon you."
"Don't even think about leaving my side. If you do, you'll be like blood separated from its vessel - nothing but a filthy puddle."
